{"tid":2329071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"元祖級藍絲上周撐777定能戰勝疫症  李偲嫣染武肺送院不治","createTime":"2020-12-17T03:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T03:46:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9fab7ad692b36e06095be46c93a0ade2e6c5b4","tid":2329071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/PPVGZLD7WRBJVOD4FPFUVNXVNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FPPVGZLD7WRBJVOD4FPFUVNXVNA%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28eoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=0dae05ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FPPVGZLD7WRBJVOD4FPFUVNXVNA%2F&h=6d6279ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/PPVGZLD7WRBJVOD4FPFUVNXVNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n元祖級藍絲上周撐777定能戰勝疫症 <br />\n李偲嫣染武肺送院不治<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】激進藍絲、正義聯盟創辦人李偲嫣昨在元朗八鄉寓所暈倒，送院不治，終年56歲，醫院證實李偲嫣初步武肺病毒檢測呈陽性，死因有待驗屍確定，並轉交死因裁判官跟進。消息指她近日發燒身體不適，以為患上傷風感冒，日前曾作病毒測試但結果呈陰性，看醫生後自行在家休養未有入院，事件中五名警員曾接觸李偲嫣及到其寓所調查，事後留在警署隔離及需接受病毒測試。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：梁美芬震驚 讚肝膽相照<br />\n<br />\n昨午12時許，李偲嫣在其元崗新村寓所房間內突然暈倒，其53歲丈夫謝鋮浚報警求助。兩名八鄉警署軍裝警員到場調查，救護。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n昨午近5時，本報記者到訪李偲嫣奶奶。。。。。。。。。「淨係話：『走咗喇』，之後都喊緊喇」。她又透露謝鋮浚早前亦有發燒，但經治療已退燒，現時正在家中隔離。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：檢測疑假陰性 留家延求診<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rjFa-vzFqLxIo_xjUHDlZHjB3Jo=/1920x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/52OZGYE6LJEPTKX2NENKIJCYO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrjFa-vzFqLxIo_xjUHDlZHjB3Jo%3D%2F1920x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F52OZGYE6LJEPTKX2NENKIJCYO4.jpg&h=d52419db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李偲嫣今年曾多次在公開場合近距離聲援鄧炳強。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交死因裁判官跟進 五警須隔離<br />\n<br />\n事後博愛醫院為李偲嫣做武肺測試，發現屬初步陽性個案。其後，另外三名包括高級督察，警署警長及高級警員穿上防護衣等到。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n博愛醫院昨晚指，搶救過程中醫護人員均穿防護裝備，沒有醫護人員被列為緊。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，李偲嫣9月29日曾趁警務處處長鄧。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣生前活躍社交媒體，本月10日更在facebook貼出宣傳林鄭抗疫短片，稱疫。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣曾任經民聯立法會議員梁美芬的非全職顧問，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W-RHqxiIy3kBKAt07wBuD-yX3KM=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F3P3H37IJBFPVHCTDPY6YA3OBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW-RHqxiIy3kBKAt07wBuD-yX3KM%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF3P3H37IJBFPVHCTDPY6YA3OBI.jpg&h=b619ca29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李偲嫣遺體昨由博愛醫院運走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZwMOkih0DjH9ffHDOeSXbAixJBM=/664x801/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PMHVP7DXANGPVEQDW6NGC67SJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZwMOkih0DjH9ffHDOeSXbAixJBM%3D%2F664x801%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPMHVP7DXANGPVEQDW6NGC67SJA.jpg&h=f6b4ef66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李本月10日在fb貼出宣傳林鄭抗疫短片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bIYbdPAPM6G4myVcCO8Otx3aJpU=/758x961/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QATRKBVJAFB2XB747TVCWRN32E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbIYbdPAPM6G4myVcCO8Otx3aJpU%3D%2F758x961%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQATRKBVJAFB2XB747TVCWRN32E.png&h=78ee1ccc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}